                  ValiBIO SA, part of VolitionRX Ltd., is a Belgian company located in Gosselies. The firm provides diagnostics services for cancer patients. Cameron John Reynolds is the CEO, in this role since 2010. On 11 Oct 10 Singapore Volition Pte Ltd. , part of VolitionRX Ltd. since October 2011, acquired ValiBIO SA from ValiRx Plc for $0.75 million.                




