Background

		Mr. Rodney Gerard Rootsaert, also known as Rod, LLB, has been a Secretary of Standard Capital Corp. since October 6, 2011. Mr. Rootsaert has been Corporate Secretary of VolitionRX Ltd since October 6, 2011. He has been an Administration and Legal Officer at VolitionRX Ltd since August 6, 2010. He has over six years of experience in providing corporate, legal and administrative services. From 2007 to 2011, he served as Corporate Secretary for several junior mining companies. ... He served as the Corporate Secretary for Magellan Copper and Gold Plc., from 2007 to 2011, where his duties included maintaining and preparing company documents, accounts and contracts. He served as Corporate Secretary for Delta Pacific Mining Plc., since 2007, where he was responsible for ensuring compliance with all relevant statutory and regulatory requirements. Mr. Rootsaert has been a Director of Mining House Ltd. since 2007.Read Full Background




